This is a collection of utilities to manipulate sac files. These programs
uses an independent library for better portability and are totally written
in C languare.

To compile it you will need:

1) make
2) cmake 

-- Optionally

3) ccmake is nice to help you configure
4) X11 libraries
5) pgplot libraries

To compile it:

% make
(choose your options)
press c-c-g
% cd build
% make
% make install

Marcelo Bianchi
